{"tid":984403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天然ㄟ尚好 網紅「香蕉妹妹」IG大方分享露毛照！","createTime":"2019-01-16T18:03:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T19:55:20.000Z","uid":212399,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5c61724e42a30a8661785740801acedab81a2920","tid":984403,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T18:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3838/d3838800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3838%2Fd3838800.jpg&h=0a36cd50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼網紅「香蕉妹妹」大方露毛，網友猛按讚！ (圖／翻攝自Instagram)<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n澳洲昆士蘭州一名美眉+素食部落客因為厭倦「西方文明世界的生活」，決心「做自己」。不久她前跑到南美洲叢林裡生活。並且記錄下自己在大自然生活裡的一點一滴。後來，她以「香蕉妹妹」(Freelee the Banana Girl)的名字把影片上傳到YouTube，還因此成為網紅。<br />\n31歲的「香蕉妹妹」表示，自己厭倦了朝九晚五的生活以及穿衣打扮。大自然的生活很好，如今的她不用化妝，單這一項就省了4000多元澳幣(約8.8萬元台幣)。為了更親近大自然，她也不大需要穿衣服，之前她還上傳過用椰子殼當胸罩的照片。她說，這個樣子讓她活得更快樂。<br />\n如今，她更宣布告別刮鬍刀，她再也不刮體毛了！關於這個，她曾經發文說：「有人吐槽我的體毛太多，我想說為什麼男人可以保留體毛，而女人不能接受真實的自己呢？ 我12歲時就開始刮腿毛。但現在我已經受夠了！」<br />\n為此，她大方把自己的「露毛照」PO上網跟大家分享。沒想到網友反應是空前的正面。有人在她的IG粉絲上留言說：「太有啟發性了」！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3838/d3838799.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3838%2Fd3838799.jpg&h=48d13bad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3838/d3838798.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3838%2Fd3838798.jpg&h=847b3b33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HIabF_hErJo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHIabF_hErJo&d=0%2F9oZcI%2F232Jiv4nLT8%2BtzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=16385267\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HIabF_hErJo</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XzDVaobz10U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXzDVaobz10U&d=0%2F9oZcI%2F232Jiv4nLT8%2BtzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=5a430f54\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XzDVaobz10U</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VgzTwjSP0Hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVgzTwjSP0Hk&d=0%2F9oZcI%2F232Jiv4nLT8%2BtzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=c399d18a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VgzTwjSP0Hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190116/1357804.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190116%2F1357804.htm&d=0%2F9oZcI%2F232Jiv4nLT8%2BtzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=2531f702\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190116/1357804.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6c5ed58942bb66ea5d2db78e0e021fb2dcc2c0ac","tid":984403,"uid":212399,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T18:06:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-cQgOv54dF7Q/W8mXYsr5ySI/AAAAAAAAAUE/a34aLDsO8_4RUnDNYwDIB8DDh_YB0RzCQCLcBGAs/s1600/C__Data_Users_DefApps_AppData_INTERNETEXPLORER_Temp_Saved%2BImages_imagesSFFPAQ75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-cQgOv54dF7Q%2FW8mXYsr5ySI%2FAAAAAAAAAUE%2Fa34aLDsO8_4RUnDNYwDIB8DDh_YB0RzCQCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2FC__Data_Users_DefApps_AppData_INTERNETEXPLORER_Temp_Saved%252BImages_imagesSFFPAQ75.jpg&h=c5f2e977&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ab1eea1c345574f77a90e4aba5b175d6cb8a394a","tid":984403,"uid":10296,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T19:36:53.000Z","msg":"31歲仲妹妹。。"},{"pid":"1e769edf1a76967539b033ea0324becbbbb2f828","tid":984403,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T19:55:20.000Z","msg":"厭倦「西方文明世界的生活」<br />\n（YouTube Facebook Instagram 除外）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}